cs.CL, cs.SI, cs.SD, cs.LG, cs.IR 

This paper deals with predicting community endorsement in online discussions, which involves natural language processing and machine learning techniques. Therefore, the most likely category is cs.CL (Computation and Language). The paper also involves the use of neural networks, which falls under the category of cs.LG (Machine Learning). The paper also deals with social media platforms, which can be categorized under cs.SI (Social and Information Networks) and cs.SD (Sound and Music Computing). Finally, the paper involves the analysis of text data, which can be categorized under cs.IR (Information Retrieval).
